Vue Macros is a collection of compile-time utilities for Vue that enhance code readability and maintainability. It introduces macros that reduce boilerplate and enable developers to leverage TypeScript more effectively. Vue Macros streamlines component development, making Vue projects cleaner and easier to manage.
